  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dobrodošli! Sada ćete naučiti brojeve od 30 do 39.</p>\n<p>Na španskom, broj 30 se zove <span class=\"highlighted-text\">treinta</span>.</p>\n<p>Brojevi od 31 do 39 formiraju se korišćenjem reči trideset <span class=\"highlighted-text\">treinta</span> (30), praćenim veznikom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">y</span> (\"na\"), zatim broja jedinica (1-9).</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Broj</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Kihispania</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">30</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">31</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y uno</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">32</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y dos</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">33</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y tres</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">34</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y cuatro</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">35</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y cinco</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">36</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y seis</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">37</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y siete</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">38</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y ocho</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">39</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y nueve</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Broj <span class=\"highlighted-text\">treinta y uno</span> (31) je jedinstven u ovom redu jer se menja u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">treinta y un</span> pre muškog imena. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Treinta y un años</span> - Trideset godina i moje.</p>\n</section>",
